{"tid":1640754,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"HKCC齊齊sit陳偉強堂","createTime":"2019-10-09T05:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T17:02:25.000Z","uid":230641,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"91b01b980c41653f9cac471f476e2b5e3bd52fc4","tid":1640754,"uid":230641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:56:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">齊齊做個勤奮好學生</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家一齊同佢交流一下中西文化的差異<br />\n佢每個禮拜五1700-1900都會響UG03上號稱再易拎grade嘅中西溝<br />\n多啲人嚟sit佢堂，鑑於目前流感高峰期，建議全部入班房嘅學生都戴好口罩，以免細菌傳播<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511633efbbd320bf9ebb675516e9b37daba7bff1","tid":1640754,"uid":230641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:59:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8df89d85b2e9b21811642d4b9c21b5cff1d43765","tid":1640754,"uid":230641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:05:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9c8e3fe957ccede9f57754de218ef0e6b6563ae","tid":1640754,"uid":279236,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:06:50.000Z","msg":"聽講琴日好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[為雙10感謝祭打開序幕]呢間餐廳大家一定要試下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640686</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"baad6e7f1a016699989152c735f1ccfb4b6bf6cf","tid":1640754,"uid":230641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:13:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5addeca23055999f85bdfc5dd6978a76c297ccca","tid":1640754,"uid":328623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:17:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae50937e63cca2d685f5fcd803370914321d199d","tid":1640754,"uid":230641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"